text = "[center][font_size=32
]
[img width=45]res://assets/img/TinyIconB.png[/img] must be following [img width=45]res://assets/img/TinyIconA.png[/img]
[img width=45]res://assets/img/TinyIconC.png[/img] must have another [img width=45]res://assets/img/TinyIconC.png[/img] 2 spaces away but never closer
[img width=45]res://assets/img/TinyIconD.png[/img] can't be closer  than 3 spaces from [img width=45]res://assets/img/TinyIconC.png[/img]
[img width=45]res://assets/img/TinyIconF.png[/img] can't be more than 3 spaces separated from [img width=45]res://assets/img/TinyIconC.png[/img]
Triple [img width=45]res://assets/img/TinyIconA.png[/img] is not allowed
[img width=45]res://assets/img/TinyIconE.png[/img] position must be multiple of 3
[img width=45]res://assets/img/TinyIconG.png[/img] must come in triplets
The symbol of 3rd position can't be next to itself
The symbol of 9th position can't be the same as 1st position
The symbol of 10th position must be the same as 1st position
The symbol of 13th position can't be the same as last position"

